nodes.label: intro
utterances: Welcome to our philosophical discussion platform. How may we assist you today?

nodes.label: metaphysics_path
utterances: Metaphysics explores the fundamental nature of reality and existence. Would you prefer to discuss the Nature of Reality or the concept of Free Will?

nodes.label: epistemology_path
utterances: Epistemology deals with the theory of knowledge. Are you interested in discussing Knowledge Acquisition or its Limitations?

nodes.label: deep_discussion
utterances: Let's delve deeper into the topic. Could you share your thoughts or questions?

nodes.label: farewell
utterances: Thank you for engaging in this philosophical discussion. Feel free to return anytime for further conversation.

nodes.label: branching_question
